<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Discipleship Bootcamp | Town Crier</title>

  <link rel="icon" type="image/png" href="/images/tcem-logo.png" />
  <link rel="apple-touch-icon" href="/images/tcem-logo.png" />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cormorant+Garamond:wght@500;600;700&family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css" />

  <style>
    .bootcamp-page {
      background: #f7f7f8;
      color: #111827;
      font-family: "Inter", sans-serif;
    }

    .bootcamp-subnav-link {
      font-family: "Inter", sans-serif;
    }

    .bootcamp-hero-label {
      font-family: "Inter", sans-serif;
      font-size: 0.88rem;
      line-height: 1;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: 0.14em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    .bootcamp-hero-title {
      font-family: "Cormorant Garamond", serif;
      font-size: clamp(3.2rem, 6vw, 5.6rem);
      line-height: 0.92;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: -0.03em;
      margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
    }

    .bootcamp-hero-text {
      font-family: "Inter", sans-serif;
      font-size: clamp(1.05rem, 2vw, 1.45rem);
      line-height: 1.8;
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.96);
    }

    .bootcamp-section-title {
      font-family: "Cormorant Garamond", serif;
      font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 4vw, 4rem);
      line-height: 0.96;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: -0.03em;
      color: #111827;
    }

    .bootcamp-card-title {
      font-family: "Cormorant Garamond", serif;
      font-size: clamp(2rem, 3vw, 2.7rem);
      line-height: 1;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: -0.02em;
      color: #111827;
    }

    .bootcamp-day-title {
      font-family: "Cormorant Garamond", serif;
      font-size: clamp(2rem, 3vw, 2.5rem);
      line-height: 1;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: -0.02em;
      color: #111827;
    }

    .bootcamp-body-text {
      font-family: "Inter", sans-serif;
      font-size: 1.05rem;
      line-height: 1.85;
      color: #475569;
    }

    .bootcamp-meta-text {
      font-family: "Inter", sans-serif;
      font-size: 1rem;
      line-height: 1.7;
      color: #64748b;
    }

    .bootcamp-button-text {
      font-family: "Inter", sans-serif;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: 0.01em;
    }

    @media (max-width: 767px) {
      .bootcamp-hero-title {
        font-size: clamp(2.7rem, 12vw, 4rem);
      }

      .bootcamp-hero-text {
        font-size: 1rem;
        line-height: 1.75;
      }

      .bootcamp-body-text {
        font-size: 1rem;
        line-height: 1.75;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body class="bootcamp-page">

  <%- include("../partials/header") %>

  <!-- MINISTRIES SUB NAV -->
  <section class="border-b border-gray-200">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 md:px-16">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-8 overflow-x-auto">
        <a href="/ministries/dbw" class="bootcamp-subnav-link inline-flex h-14 items-center border-b-2 border-transparent text-gray-700 font-medium hover:text-[#4F46E5] whitespace-nowrap transition">
          Discipleship by the Word
        </a>
        <a href="/ministries/bootcamp" class="bootcamp-subnav-link inline-flex h-14 items-center border-b-2 border-[#4F46E5] text-[#4F46E5] font-semibold whitespace-nowrap">
          Discipleship Bootcamp
        </a>
        <a href="/ministries/arrows" class="bootcamp-subnav-link inline-flex h-14 items-center border-b-2 border-transparent text-gray-700 font-medium hover:text-[#4F46E5] whitespace-nowrap transition">
          Arrows in the Quiver
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- HERO -->
  <section class="py-12 md:py-14">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 md:px-16">
      <div class="rounded-[30px] bg-gradient-to-r from-[#FF6A00] via-[#FF4D4D] to-[#EC4899] px-8 md:px-12 py-12 md:py-16 text-white shadow-sm">
        <div class="max-w-4xl">
          <span class="bootcamp-hero-label inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full bg-white/20 px-4 py-2 mb-6">
            <span class="text-base">⚡</span>
            Intensive Training
          </span>

          <h1 class="bootcamp-hero-title">
            Discipleship Bootcamp
          </h1>

          <p class="bootcamp-hero-text">
            Holy Ghost Bootcamp, also referred to as HBC KWASU, is a bootcamp-style discipleship and revival meeting organized by Town Crier Evangelical Ministries. It reflects TCEM’s mandate of discipleship, revival, and evangelical missions, bringing believers together for concentrated sessions of prayer, teaching, consecration, and spiritual awakening.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- WHAT IS BOOTCAMP + WHY ATTEND -->
  <section class="pb-12 md:pb-14">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 md:px-16">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-8">

        <div class="bg-white border border-gray-100 rounded-[28px] shadow-sm p-8 md:p-10">
          <h2 class="bootcamp-section-title mb-6">
  What is <span class="italic">Bootcamp?</span>
</h2>

          <div class="space-y-6">
            <p class="bootcamp-body-text">
              Discipleship Bootcamp is an intensive, concentrated training experience where participants are immersed in biblical teaching, worship, prayer, and practical ministry exercises over three consecutive days.
            </p>

            <p class="bootcamp-body-text">
              Unlike regular classes that meet weekly, Bootcamp provides focused, uninterrupted time to dive deep into God's Word and develop critical ministry skills in a supportive, high-energy environment.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white border border-gray-100 rounded-[28px] shadow-sm p-8 md:p-10">
          <h2 class="bootcamp-section-title mb-6">
            Why Attend?
          </h2>

          <div class="space-y-4">
            <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
              <span class="text-2xl text-green-500 mt-0.5">✅</span>
              <p class="bootcamp-body-text">Accelerated spiritual growth in just 3 days</p>
            </div>

            <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
              <span class="text-2xl text-green-500 mt-0.5">✅</span>
              <p class="bootcamp-body-text">Intensive biblical teaching from experienced leaders</p>
            </div>

            <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
              <span class="text-2xl text-green-500 mt-0.5">✅</span>
              <p class="bootcamp-body-text">Hands-on ministry practice and activation</p>
            </div>

            <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
              <span class="text-2xl text-green-500 mt-0.5">✅</span>
              <p class="bootcamp-body-text">Deep fellowship with like-minded believers</p>
            </div>

            <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
              <span class="text-2xl text-green-500 mt-0.5">✅</span>
              <p class="bootcamp-body-text">Breakthrough in prayer and worship</p>
            </div>

            <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
              <span class="text-2xl text-green-500 mt-0.5">✅</span>
              <p class="bootcamp-body-text">Practical tools for effective ministry</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- DAILY SCHEDULE -->
  <section class="py-8 md:py-10">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 md:px-16">
      <div class="text-center mb-10">
        <h2 class="bootcamp-section-title">
          Daily Schedule
        </h2>
      </div>

      <div class="overflow-hidden rounded-[28px] border border-gray-100 bg-white shadow-sm">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 divide-y md:divide-y-0 md:divide-x divide-gray-100">

          <div class="p-8 md:p-10">
            <h3 class="bootcamp-day-title text-center mb-1">Day 1</h3>
            <p class="text-center text-[#4F46E5] text-xl font-semibold mb-6">Foundations</p>

            <ul class="space-y-4 bootcamp-body-text">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><span class="text-[#4F46E5] mt-1">•</span> Biblical Identity</li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><span class="text-[#4F46E5] mt-1">•</span> Prayer Life</li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><span class="text-[#4F46E5] mt-1">•</span> Hearing God's Voice</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="p-8 md:p-10">
            <h3 class="bootcamp-day-title text-center mb-1">Day 2</h3>
            <p class="text-center text-[#4F46E5] text-xl font-semibold mb-6">Growth</p>

            <ul class="space-y-4 bootcamp-body-text">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><span class="text-[#4F46E5] mt-1">•</span> Spiritual Disciplines</li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><span class="text-[#4F46E5] mt-1">•</span> Ministry Gifts</li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><span class="text-[#4F46E5] mt-1">•</span> Evangelism Skills</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="p-8 md:p-10">
            <h3 class="bootcamp-day-title text-center mb-1">Day 3</h3>
            <p class="text-center text-[#4F46E5] text-xl font-semibold mb-6">Activation</p>

            <ul class="space-y-4 bootcamp-body-text">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><span class="text-[#4F46E5] mt-1">•</span> Leadership Training</li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><span class="text-[#4F46E5] mt-1">•</span> Ministry Practice</li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><span class="text-[#4F46E5] mt-1">•</span> Commissioning</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-6 rounded-[24px] bg-slate-50 border border-gray-100 p-6 md:p-8">
        <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
          <span class="text-2xl text-[#4F46E5]">🕒</span>
          <div>
            <h3 class="bootcamp-card-title mb-2">
              Time: 10:00 AM - 4:00 PM Daily
            </h3>
            <p class="bootcamp-body-text">
              Includes morning worship, teaching sessions, lunch, workshops, and evening activation
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- 2026 DATES -->
  <section class="pt-12 md:pt-14 pb-8">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 md:px-16">
      <div class="text-center mb-10">
        <h2 class="bootcamp-section-title">
          2026 Bootcamp Dates
        </h2>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 xl:grid-cols-4 gap-6">

        <div class="bg-white border border-orange-200 rounded-[26px] shadow-sm p-8 text-center">
          <div class="w-14 h-14 mx-auto rounded-full bg-orange-100 flex items-center justify-center text-2xl mb-6">📅</div>
          <h3 class="bootcamp-card-title mb-2">Q1 Bootcamp</h3>
          <p class="bootcamp-body-text mb-5">March 15-17, 2026</p>
          <span class="inline-flex rounded-full bg-green-100 text-green-700 px-4 py-1.5 text-sm font-semibold">
            Upcoming
          </span>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white border border-gray-100 rounded-[26px] shadow-sm p-8 text-center">
          <div class="w-14 h-14 mx-auto rounded-full bg-orange-100 flex items-center justify-center text-2xl mb-6">📅</div>
          <h3 class="bootcamp-card-title mb-2">Q2 Bootcamp</h3>
          <p class="bootcamp-body-text mb-5">June 10-12, 2026</p>
          <span class="inline-flex rounded-full bg-green-100 text-green-700 px-4 py-1.5 text-sm font-semibold">
            Open
          </span>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white border border-gray-100 rounded-[26px] shadow-sm p-8 text-center">
          <div class="w-14 h-14 mx-auto rounded-full bg-orange-100 flex items-center justify-center text-2xl mb-6">📅</div>
          <h3 class="bootcamp-card-title mb-2">Q3 Bootcamp</h3>
          <p class="bootcamp-body-text mb-5">September 5-7, 2026</p>
          <span class="inline-flex rounded-full bg-green-100 text-green-700 px-4 py-1.5 text-sm font-semibold">
            Open
          </span>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white border border-gray-100 rounded-[26px] shadow-sm p-8 text-center">
          <div class="w-14 h-14 mx-auto rounded-full bg-orange-100 flex items-center justify-center text-2xl mb-6">📅</div>
          <h3 class="bootcamp-card-title mb-2">Q4 Bootcamp</h3>
          <p class="bootcamp-body-text mb-5">December 1-3, 2026</p>
          <span class="inline-flex rounded-full bg-green-100 text-green-700 px-4 py-1.5 text-sm font-semibold">
            Open
          </span>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- WHAT TO BRING + REGISTRATION -->
  <section class="py-12 md:py-14">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 md:px-16">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-8">

        <div class="rounded-[28px] border border-indigo-200 bg-indigo-50/70 p-8 md:p-10">
          <h2 class="bootcamp-section-title mb-6">
            What to Bring
          </h2>

          <ul class="space-y-4 bootcamp-body-text">
            <li>• Your Bible and notebook</li>
            <li>• Pen and highlighters</li>
            <li>• Open heart and expectant faith</li>
            <li>• Lunch or food budget</li>
            <li>• Questions and testimonies to share</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="rounded-[28px] border border-orange-100 bg-orange-50/40 p-8 md:p-10">
          <h2 class="bootcamp-section-title mb-6">
            Registration
          </h2>

          <div class="space-y-6">
            <p class="bootcamp-body-text">
              Early bird registration closes 2 weeks before each bootcamp. Space is limited to ensure quality interaction.
            </p>

            <p class="bootcamp-card-title">
              Fee: ₦5,000 (includes materials &amp; lunch)
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="pt-4 pb-20 md:pb-24">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 md:px-16">
      <div class="rounded-[30px] bg-gradient-to-r from-[#FF6A00] via-[#FF5A4D] to-[#EC4899] px-8 md:px-12 py-12 md:py-14 text-white text-center shadow-sm">
       <h2 class="bootcamp-section-title text-white mb-5">
  Register for Next Bootcamp
</h2>

        <p class="bootcamp-hero-text max-w-4xl mx-auto mb-8">
          Don't miss this transformative experience. Secure your spot today!
        </p>

        <a
          href="/contact?type=registration&target=Discipleship%20Bootcamp#contact-form-section"
          class="bootcamp-button-text inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-3 rounded-2xl bg-white text-[#FF5A00] px-8 py-4 text-lg shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition min-w-[190px]"
        >
          Register Now
          <span class="text-2xl leading-none">→</span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <%- include("../partials/auth-modal") %>
  <script src="/js/auth-modal.js"></script>

</body>
</html>